SELECT po.owner_name, po.contact_email, pt.property_type FROM property_owners po JOIN property_types pt ON po.property_id = pt.property_id WHERE po.contact_email LIKE '%gmail.com' ORDER BY po.owner_name ASC;

SELECT pl.location, pi.image_url, pt.property_type FROM property_listings pl JOIN property_images pi ON pl.property_id = pi.property_id JOIN property_types pt ON pl.property_id = pt.property_id WHERE pt.property_type = 'Apartment' ORDER BY pl.location DESC, pi.image_url ASC, pt.property_type ASC;
